{
  "texts": [
    "There was no one to answer my questions.",
    "I found that very, very hard, especially the first few weeks.",
    "[INT 5] I really need someone who'll say, \"Go, we'll do this, we'll do that.\"",
    "In writing, I'll read, and I'll say to myself, \"Oh my god, that's wonderful,\" but I'll do it 2 or 3 times, and then I'll give up...",
    "But I've always been like that; I've always needed someone to push me, not in everything, but especially since I've been ill. [INT 9]There are participants who related less to parts of the program because their activity level was not adequately represented: We always assume that people aren't physically active when in pain."
  ]
}